item.title: ResInsight 1.4.0 Released
item.description: We are happy to announce the release of ResInsight v1.4.0 which is a maintenance release. It also serves as an alignment of the codebase with the efforts done to add Geomechanical support to ResInsight. Download Have a look at the GitHub release-page to read the release-notes or to download the new release: Release v1.4.0 on GitHub
